# 🖥️ StudyVault Frontend — Bug Audit Report

> Đọc toàn bộ source code frontend mới nhất. Kiểm tra từng file page, service, route guard, context, utility.

---

## Tổng quan

| Module | Files đã đọc | Kết quả |
|---|---|---|
| Pages | Login, Register, Profile, ForgotPassword, WorkspacePage, DocumentViewer, Admin | ✅ |
| API Services | apiClient.js, authAPI, documentAPI, ragAPI, folderAPI, adminAPI, tagAPI | ✅ |
| Route Guards | ProtectedWorkspaceRoute, GuestOnlyRoute | ✅ |
| Context/Utils | DocViewerContext, auth.js, apiError.js, workspaceNavigation | ✅ |

